      "content": "that's a good start. i'm trying to get more specific with the tension though. like, if the protagonist is an outsider, could the \"vibe\" of the neighborhood be tied to the idea that the community is inherently more aggressive or prone to sudden violence? i want to capture that feeling where you feel like any corner you turn could lead to a confrontation or something much darker just because of the energy of the area. how can i use that to make the reader feel like they're actually in danger?",
